llah-deputy-chief-says-israel-must-stop-gaza-war-for-combat-in-lebanon-to-end/0000018c-c066-d6c4-ab8d-e1f600220000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列精神卫生系统面临崩溃，数十名精神科医生前往英国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-system-in-israel-collapses-psychiatrists-are-leaving-for-britain/0000018c-c026-d3e0-abac-d8af89aa0000</link><description>消息人士将人才外流归因于工作量不断增加，并认为情况只会恶化，因为卫生部修复该系统的计划仍在等待财政部的资金批准</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 15:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-system-in-israel-collapses-psychiatrists-are-leaving-for-britain/0000018c-c026-d3e0-abac-d8af89aa0000</guid></item><item><title>一名加沙男孩梦想打破互联网。他做到了——在以色列炸弹炸死他之后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/a-gaza-boy-dreamed-of-breaking-the-internet-he-did-after-an-israeli-bomb-killed-him/0000018c-bfcb-d4e1-ad8f-bffbc01b0000</link><description>13 岁的 Awni Eldous 经营着一个 YouTube 频道，梦想成为一名有影响力的人。他的故事在世界各地引起共鸣，代表了加沙儿童在战争中的悲剧</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 14:48:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/a-gaza-boy-dreamed-of-breaking-the-internet-he-did-after-an-israeli-bomb-killed-him/0000018c-bfcb-d4e1-ad8f-bffbc01b0000</guid></item><item><title>“100-20万，而不是200万”：以色列财政部长设想加沙人口减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/100-200-000-not-two-million-israels-finance-minister-envisions-depopulated-gaza/0000018c-bfe8-d6c4-ab8d-fffc0b910000</link><description>以色列极右翼财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇与越来越多的高级立法者一起表示支持大规模转移加沙平民，以解决以色列战后安全问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 14:46:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/100-200-000-not-two-million-israels-finance-minister-envisions-depopulated-gaza/0000018c-bfe8-d6c4-ab8d-fffc0b910000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列的支持就没有红线吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-there-no-red-lines-to-u-s-support-for-israel/0000018c-bf3a-d45c-a98e-bf7ea92b0000</link><description>10月7日是一起令人发指的罪行。但是，有多少加沙人必须死去，有多少以色列部长必须推动种族清洗，内塔尼​​亚胡必须否认多少失败——美国才能重新考虑其对以色列政府发动的邪恶战争的不道德、无条件的支持？</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-there-no-red-lines-to-u-s-support-for-israel/0000018c-bf3a-d45c-a98e-bf7ea92b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争，以色列内阁投票决定将地方选举推迟至二月下旬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-votes-to-delay-local-elections-until-late-february-due-to-gaza-war/0000018c-bffd-d6c4-ab8d-fffd56ab0000</link><description>以色列国防军数据显示，数百名候选人在预备役中服役，无法被释放，选举第二次推迟，但代表预备役候选人的律师表示，推迟选举“具有讽刺意味的是，这增加了对手的优势”</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-votes-to-delay-local-elections-until-late-february-due-to-gaza-war/0000018c-bffd-d6c4-ab8d-fffd56ab0000</guid></item><item><title>赛车无人机军备竞赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/the-racing-drones-arms-race/0000018c-bf91-d6c4-ab8d-ffb5243a0000</link><description>FPV 无人机凭借 150 公里/小时的疯狂机动性，已成为乌克兰战场上精确、致命的制导武器。对他们的防御是有限的。他们很快就会出现在我们的舞台上吗？以色列准备好了吗？</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/the-racing-drones-arms-race/0000018c-bf91-d6c4-ab8d-ffb5243a0000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争而延长学年，大多数以色列大学都开始学年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/following-delays-academic-school-year-begins-at-most-israeli-universities/0000018c-bfd3-d6c4-ab8d-fff7a61a0000</link><description>课程于周日开始，比原计划晚了大约两个半月，并且没有预备役人员。 ■ 学术机构与军队之间达成的一项协议，为仍在预备役的 58,000 名学生和教师制定了调整框架</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/following-delays-academic-school-year-begins-at-most-israeli-universities/0000018c-bfd3-d6c4-ab8d-fff7a61a0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-bfd2-d4e1-ad8f-bff360880000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，自10月7日以来，以色列士兵在战斗中丧生的人数为506人</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 12:55:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-bfd2-d4e1-ad8f-bff360880000</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷总统宣布“对以色列国和犹太人民的坚定承诺”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/argentina-president-declares-unalterable-commitment-to-israel-and-the-jewish-people/0000018c-bfb4-d6c4-ab8d-ffb445f20000</link><description>总统哈维尔·米莱被广泛认为是亲以色列的极右民粹主义者，他对犹太教很着迷，甚至谈到了跟随拉比学习并有可能皈依该宗教</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 12:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/argentina-president-declares-unalterable-commitment-to-israel-and-the-jewish-people/0000018c-bfb4-d6c4-ab8d-ffb445f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部度假胜地埃拉特发现迷路的阿拉斯加潜鸟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/very-lost-alaskan-loon-spotted-in-southern-israeli-resort-of-eilat/0000018c-bfb3-d4e1-ad8f-bfb3c7ac0000</link><description>这是中东地区首次出现的此类事件。观鸟专家约夫·帕尔曼表示，太平洋潜鸟可能被风暴吹过大西洋，然后错误地转向南方</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 12:18:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/very-lost-alaskan-loon-spotted-in-southern-israeli-resort-of-eilat/0000018c-bfb3-d4e1-ad8f-bfb3c7ac0000</guid></item><item><title>这些令人心碎的照片证明：以色列是一个艰难的地方</title><link>h